         "Vegetarian [in] mouth [but] not vegetarian [at] heart"
         (said of vegetarians that eat imitation meat).
       ==
    1. Plain, pure, etc.
       ==
       - 齋啡 (zaai1 fe1): "Straight coffee."
       - 齋腸 (zaai1 coeng4-2): "Plain [rice-noodle] roll."
       - 齋噏 (zaai1 ngap1): "Purely blabbering."
       ==
    ++
  - 【話齋】 (waa6 zaai1):
